        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You fire blasts of solar energy through your raised shield, harnessing its gravitational force to propel your attacks. When you make a solar flare Strike while you have your solar shield raised, increase the range increment of your solar flare by 10 feet and increase the damage your solar flare deals by 1 per weapon damage die.</p>\n<p><strong>Graviton-Attuned</strong> The additional damage is bludgeoning damage. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Trip] attempt on a critical success.</p>\n<p><strong>Photon-Attuned</strong> The additional damage is fire damage. Increase the persistent fire damage on a critical success to 1d8.</p>"
